reviews.comment: I choose this person because he had a 1 day turn around and not many people in his que.  However it took us over a week to get an acceptable product.

I enjoyed working with Sumon, but there were a few issues. Sumon is great at what he does and will honor the unlimited revisions. He has a great response time and does a great job of aligning everything with the brand. Besides this, I am not too happy with his attention to detail. It seems that he rushed a bit. Other than that, I would suggest working with Sumon, but make sure you give specific information and a ton of direction and use unlimited revisions.

I asked him to make a revision 3 times and he never made the change. He kept saying he needed to sleep. This was 3 days in a row.  I also asked for the source file. I figured I could make the change myself and he sent me a file I could not edit.  I tried in Illustrator and Photoshop.  THe cover page for Facebook looked good, he just did not make the edits I asked for.  Unfortunately I had to use it the way it was because I am running ads.

He is creative in his work and can understand your request and analyze it to reach your goal. And more than that, he has a great talent, and I will advise and tell people in the future to deal with him because he deserves that and more.

Sumon has demonstrated excellent skills in creating Facebook ads, achieving remarkable performance with a CTR of around 4%. His ability to attract customers is evident, and he has shown a thorough understanding of what captures their interest.
